{"type": "article", "id": 19585, "title": "全球最棒的平面设计公司，42年来做的纪念卡片都在这里", "description": "它们每年都以此作为礼物送给客户或者伙伴。42年，你也能看出诸多变迁。", "date": "2015-12-24T10:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 10666, "name": "Pentagram"}, {"id": 20507, "name": "贺卡"}, {"id": 20896, "name": "42年"}, {"id": 20897, "name": "设计史"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 587, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703181246IJaZ6y5RbLx7NKiS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t五角国际设计事务所（Pentagram）成立于 1972 年，是一家很有历史的设计公司。从 1974 年起，每年年末，他们都会设计一些小册子和卡片，送给客户、朋友和同事们。到今年，这些册子已连续推出 41 年了，所以卡片积攒了五花八门的主题，从食谱到折纸指南，从星座到个性化字体。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t说五角设计是家公司，倒不如说它是一个设计联盟。它前身是五十年代末期成立的“ Fletcher 与 Forbes ”公司，创始人是 Alan Fletcher 和 Colin Forbes 。经过一些年的发展，这间小公司开始接纳新的合作伙伴，并将公司名字改为五角设计（Pentagram），主要从事平面、建筑和工业设计。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tPentagram 采取平等合作的原则，加入公司的设计师都属于合伙人，他们彼此独立，各自负责自己的设计小组和项目。这些年，新加入公司的设计师大多是在行业内已树立了一定名声、在业务上已有实际经验的人。目前公司的合伙人有 19 位。如今他们在伦敦、纽约、旧金山和和奥斯汀等地设有 5 个工作室，做了许多大型项目。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t如文章开头所说，Pentagram 的新年问候非常有趣，是通过卡片传达的。“我们的卡片强调的是家庭团聚的趣味性，绝对、绝对不是为了推销自己。”\r\n合伙人之一的 Michael Bierut 说，他从 1990 年起就开始在 Pentagram 工作了。每一年，19 位合伙人中的一人会承担卡片的设计工作，他先是在全体大会上提出粗略提案，大家提意见，该设计师再在几个月后的秋季会议上提交最终版本。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t2009 年，设计师 John Rushworth 和 Naresh Ramchandani 设计了与卡片相对应的性格字体测验； 2010 年，设计师 Angus Hyland 设计了一个优雅的小册子，它是一种罕见的字谜，可以供全家人合作着玩；而今年，<a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3040154/40-years-of-pentagrams-wonderfully-creative-holiday-cards\" target=\"_blank\">Angus Hyland 和他的团队再次承载了设计卡片的任务</a>，来看看过去 41 年里的卡片吧：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181226u5rtJQLN3kVqIHOM.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1974 Matches (John McConnell)\" alt=\"1974 Matches (John McConnell)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1974\tMatches (John McConnell)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181227qfQRdmAgSNby1h2e.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1975 A Book of Rhyming Slang (Mervyn Kurlansky)\" alt=\"1975 A Book of Rhyming Slang (Mervyn Kurlansky)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1975\tA Book of Rhyming Slang (Mervyn Kurlansky)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181227GB3FipoxUDvEn4WQ.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1976 Patience Games for Playing Cards (Alan Fletcher)\" alt=\"1976 Patience Games for Playing Cards (Alan Fletcher)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1976\tPatience Games for Playing Cards (Alan Fletcher)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181227Pnf3hlAUTzBpYumw.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1977 Cocktails (John McConnell)\" alt=\"1977 Cocktails (John McConnell)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1977\tCocktails (John McConnell)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181228oHi6ekPhvxrWlE2u.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1978 An A-Z of Limericks (Alan Fletcher)\" alt=\"1978 An A-Z of Limericks (Alan Fletcher)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1978 An A-Z of Limericks (Alan Fletcher)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181229q4xMrlvLghKipBmT.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1979 Science Amusante (Alan Fletcher)\" alt=\"1979 Science Amusante (Alan Fletcher)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1979 Science Amusante (Alan Fletcher)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181229X5R4hVF8oNyaeDPM.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1980 Take a Piece of String (David Hillman)\" alt=\"1980 Take a Piece of String (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1980 Take a Piece of String (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181230CbLmYQ5SygKspkv6.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1981 Six Ways to Fold a Table-Napkin (John McConnell)\" alt=\"1981 Six Ways to Fold a Table-Napkin (John McConnell)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1981 Six Ways to Fold a Table-Napkin (John McConnell)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812308vHbpP0BwOzU9uYk.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1982 Mora: The Play of Love (Mervyn Kurlansky)\" alt=\"1982 Mora: The Play of Love (Mervyn Kurlansky)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1982\tMora: The Play of Love (Mervyn Kurlansky)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812300WwEKVpJr2mPi4vq.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1983 Yours Sincerely (Colin Forbes)\" alt=\"1983 Yours Sincerely (Colin Forbes)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1983 Yours Sincerely (Colin Forbes)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181231VE2JqwOlNTRSs4Uf.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1984 A Fortunate Hand (David Hillman)\" alt=\"1984 A Fortunate Hand (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1984\tA Fortunate Hand (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181232aSwUJKuVsITyMdWl.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1985 Paper Airplanes (John McConnell)\" alt=\"1985 Paper Airplanes (John McConnell)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1985\tPaper Airplanes (John McConnell)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181232alDs3HJQIdFB7NwO.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1986 Paper Puzzles (David Hillman)\" alt=\"1986 Paper Puzzles (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1986\tPaper Puzzles (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812338GwMKQjzmVIhL3f2.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1987 Six Domino Puzzles (David Hillman)\" alt=\"1987 Six Domino Puzzles (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1987\tSix Domino Puzzles (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181233fRsBTIOdnZx7XVzK.jpg\" width=\"746\" height=\"500\" title=\"1988 Chinese Horoscopes (Mervyn Kurlansky)\" alt=\"1988 Chinese Horoscopes (Mervyn Kurlansky)\" data-ratio=\"0.67024129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1988\tChinese Horoscopes (Mervyn Kurlansky)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181234qSUpaKhTm3uzkMGC.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1989 Thirteen Ways to Tempt Fate (John Rushworth)\" alt=\"1989 Thirteen Ways to Tempt Fate (John Rushworth)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1989 Thirteen Ways to Tempt Fate (John Rushworth)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181234ylbGPK80qdgsaEH9.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1990 How to Remember Not to Forget (John Rushworth)\" alt=\"1990 How to Remember Not to Forget (John Rushworth)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1990\tHow to Remember Not to Forget (John Rushworth)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181235tDQBZvgPw6Mub9Uj.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1991 Identify Thirteen Mystery Objects (John Rushworth)\" alt=\"1991 Identify Thirteen Mystery Objects (John Rushworth)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1991\tIdentify Thirteen Mystery Objects (John Rushworth)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181235kifIERTaMm6evVOH.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1992 L’Enfance de la Cuisine (Michael Bierut)\" alt=\"1992 L’Enfance de la Cuisine (Michael Bierut)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1992\tL’Enfance de la Cuisine (Michael Bierut)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812352fTEDa3PwgOHVhNX.jpg\" width=\"746\" height=\"500\" title=\"1993 First Draw Your Circle (David Hillman)\" alt=\"1993 First Draw Your Circle (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.67024129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1993\tFirst Draw Your Circle (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181236NPFJadLD37vZlAQH.jpg\" width=\"746\" height=\"500\" title=\"1994 How Good Is Your Taste? (Michael Gericke)\" alt=\"1994 How Good Is Your Taste? (Michael Gericke)\" data-ratio=\"0.67024129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1994\tHow Good Is Your Taste? (Michael Gericke)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812369t2GRT07vDYxU6eI.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1995 The Pressman’s Hat (John McConnell)\" alt=\"1995 The Pressman’s Hat (John McConnell)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1995\tThe Pressman’s Hat (John McConnell)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181237asbF3dUG1oYik2ES.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1996 Six Tunes for Eight Wine Bottles (John McConnell)\" alt=\"1996 Six Tunes for Eight Wine Bottles (John McConnell)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1996 Six Tunes for Eight Wine Bottles (John McConnell)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070318123740zDaOvq5utSn2E9.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1997 AL for Bet (John McConnell)\" alt=\"1997 AL for Bet (John McConnell)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1997\tAL for Bet (John McConnell)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181238iLXayt5qSkxOFEn4.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1998 Ladle Rat Rotten Hut (Michael Bierut)\" alt=\"1998 Ladle Rat Rotten Hut (Michael Bierut)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1998\tLadle Rat Rotten Hut (Michael Bierut)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181238kWHIoivh2yKwAe47.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"1999 Crossword (John McConnell)\" alt=\"1999 Crossword (John McConnell)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>1999 Crossword (John McConnell)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812396dl9QfPYeAHpknLw.jpg\" width=\"748\" height=\"500\" title=\"2000 All the King’s Horses (John McConnell)\" alt=\"2000 All the King’s Horses (John McConnell)\" data-ratio=\"0.6684492\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2000\tAll the King’s Horses (John McConnell)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812407fn1QazBsOKGlUb6.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2001 Why do you say that? (David Hillman)\" alt=\"2001 Why do you say that? (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2001\tWhy do you say that? (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181240C4zsQEbtPjiON9gX.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2002 Fitting Words (David Hillman)\" alt=\"2002 Fitting Words (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2002\tFitting Words (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812407j9iM4kydKZXCRnh.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2003 I’m afraid I have a phobia (David Hillman)\" alt=\"2003 I’m afraid I have a phobia (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2003 I’m afraid I have a phobia (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812410jEQzhZON68qcrvT.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2004 Collective Wisdom (David Hillman)\" alt=\"2004 Collective Wisdom (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2004\tCollective Wisdom (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181241Ve6MFxKI08mjkWoq.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2005 Alpha to Zulu (David Hillman)\" alt=\"2005 Alpha to Zulu (David Hillman)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2005\tAlpha to Zulu (David Hillman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181242YzgQ9ZTJfGu3l8VU.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2006 The Alphabet: A Critical Assessment (Michael Bierut)\" alt=\"2006 The Alphabet: A Critical Assessment (Michael Bierut)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2006 The Alphabet: A Critical Assessment (Michael Bierut)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181242ok6iNxRh4DXFfrpB.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2007 Decipher (Harry Pearce)\" alt=\"2007 Decipher (Harry Pearce)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2007 Decipher (Harry Pearce)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181243lw0fX2UtV9hbi5Rm.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2008 A Number of Numbers (Michael Gericke)\" alt=\"2008 A Number of Numbers (Michael Gericke)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2008 A Number of Numbers (Michael Gericke)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031812432cP9oFRKkXB1Osvh.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2009 What Type Are You? (John Rushworth)\" alt=\"2009 What Type Are You? (John Rushworth)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2009\tWhat Type Are You? (John Rushworth)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181243M18mW7eGxP9Tk5Cs.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2010 See Opposite (Angus Hyland)\" alt=\"2010 See Opposite (Angus Hyland)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2010 See Opposite (Angus Hyland)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181244KEVqAWLdr4U2z8it.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2011 Today I’m Feeling Turquoise (Domenic Lippa, Naresh Ramchandani)\" alt=\"2011 Today I’m Feeling Turquoise (Domenic Lippa, Naresh Ramchandani)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2011\tToday I’m Feeling Turquoise (Domenic Lippa, Naresh Ramchandani)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181244gA3QJYdKnusei8tj.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"500\" title=\"2012 Darling, I got you a paperclip (Naresh Ramchandani, John Rushworth)\" alt=\"2012 Darling, I got you a paperclip (Naresh Ramchandani, John Rushworth)\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2012\tDarling, I got you a paperclip (Naresh Ramchandani, John Rushworth)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181245dKeo71imHM5xYp6O.jpg\" width=\"674\" height=\"500\" title=\"2013 Coyote v. Acme (Michael Bierut)\" alt=\"2013 Coyote v. Acme (Michael Bierut)\" data-ratio=\"0.74183976\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2013 Coyote v. Acme (Michael Bierut)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181245uF48cKEZNQWd65Ag.jpg\" width=\"674\" height=\"500\" title=\"2014\" alt=\"2014\" data-ratio=\"0.74183976\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2014</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181245wRKtVeTEXxn9kgy6.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" title=\"2015\" alt=\"2015\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>2015</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3040154/40-years-of-pentagrams-wonderfully-creative-holiday-cards#1\" target=\"_blank\">fastcodesign</a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}